hotel%20to%20another%20without%20staying%20put%20for%20more%20than%20a%20day%20or%20two%20at%20a%20time.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EShe%20says%20you%20can%C2%A0save%20money%20on%20travel%20by%20choosing%20one%20place%20as%20your%20base%20and%20doing%20day%20trips%20from%20there%20rather%20than%20burning%20through%20cash%20(and%20time)%20on%20a%20train%20or%20plane%20every%20few%20days.%20You%20may%20also%20be%20able%20to%20get%20a%20better%20deal%20on%20a%20short-term%20apartment%20rental%20with%20a%20weekly%20rate%20versus%20a%20hotel%20stay%2C%C2%A0and%20you%20can%20save%20money%20by%20preparing%20some%20of%20your%20own%20meals.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E2.%20Not%20checking%20their%20credit%20card%20for%20fees%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EFinancial%20educator%20Nia%20Adams%20says%20far%20too%20many%20travelers%20never%20think%20about%20extra%20fees%20they%20may%20have%20to%20pay%20to%20use%20their%20credit%20card%20or%20debit%20card%20overseas.%20The%20biggest%20of%20these%20fees%20is%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpersonal-finance%2Fcredit-cards%2Fwhat-is-foreign-transaction-fee%5C%22%3Eforeign%20transaction%20fees%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20which%20typically%20tack%20on%20around%203%25%20on%20every%20purchase%20made%20outside%20the%20United%20States.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BDepending%20on%20the%20bank%20or%20credit%20card%20terms%2C%20foreign%20transaction%20fees%20can%20really%20add%20up%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETo%20avoid%20these%20fees%2C%20consumers%20can%20apply%20for%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpersonal-finance%2Fbest-credit-cards-no-foreign-transaction-fees%5C%22%3Ecredit%20card%20with%20no%20foreign%20transaction%20fees%3C%2Fa%3E%20early%20enough%20to%20get%20it%20in%20their%20hands%20before%20an%20international%20trip.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E3.%20Not%20using%20a%20travel%20agent%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EPlanning%20your%20own%20trip%20can%20make%20travel%20more%20stressful%20and%20confusing%2C%20but%20it%20can%20also%20cost%20you%20more%20money%20in%20the%20end.%20That's%20part%20of%20the%20reason%20so%20many%20consumers%20use%20a%20travel%20agent%20to%20help%20them%20figure%20out%20the%20phases%20of%20their%20trip%20while%20securing%20the%20best%20pricing%20on%20everything%20from%20hotels%20to%20tours.%20Many%20travel%20agents%20even%20offer%20their%20services%20for%20free.%20They%20get%20paid%20commissions%20for%20accommodations%20and%20professional%20tours%20they%20book%20on%20their%20client's%20behalf.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20travel%20agent%20Krissy%20Yoder%20of%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.beourguesttravelcompany.com%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EBe%20Our%20Guest%20Travel%20Company%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20using%20a%20trusted%20travel%20advisor%20is%20the%20key%20to%20avoiding%20making%20many%20costly%20mistakes.%20%26quot%3BA%20travel%20professional%20can%20guide%20their%20clients%20through%20the%20options%20and%20make%20sure%20they%20are%20comfortable%20with%20the%20inclusions%20in%20their%20package%20and%20that%20they%20understand%20other%20costs%20they%20may%20incur.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E4.%20Traveling%20without%20health%20coverage%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3ETravel%20agent%20Erica%20Wood%20of%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.daybreaktravelco.com%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EDaybreak%20Travel%20Co.%3C%2Fa%3E%20says%20many%20travelers%20don't%20realize%20their%20health%20insurance%20typically%20doesn't%20follow%20them%20to%20other%20countries.%20Then%2C%20if%20something%20unfortunate%20happens%2C%20they%20wind%20up%20with%20thousands%20of%20dollars%20(and%20potentially%20more)%20in%20unexpected%20medical%20bills.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BA%20broken%20bone%2C%20heart%20attack%2C%20and%20more%20would%20all%20need%20to%20be%20paid%20out%20of%20pocket%20during%20travel%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Wood.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOn%20the%20flipside%20of%20that%2C%20buying%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpersonal-finance%2Ftravel-insurance%2Fhow-much-do-i-need-travel-medical-insurance%5C%22%3Etravel%20medical%20insurance%3C%2Fa%3E%20ahead%20of%20time%20can%20ensure%20you%20get%20the%20care%20you%20need%20without%20ruining%20your%20finances.%20Most%20travel%20insurance%20policies%20offer%20at%20least%20%2415%2C000%20or%20%2425%2C000%20in%20coverage%20for%20emergency%20medical%20expenses%20that%20can%20apply%20overseas%2C%20but%20you%20can%20also%20find%20policies%20with%20much%20higher%20limits%20for%20medical%20coverage.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E5.%20Not%20investing%20in%20a%20broad%20travel%20insurance%20policy%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EOther%20inclusions%20in%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpersonal-finance%2Ftravel-insurance%2Fbest-travel-insurance-companies%5C%22%3Etravel%20insurance%20plan%3C%2Fa%3E%20can%20prove%20crucial.%20For%20example%2C%20these%20plans%20can%20provide%20coverage%20for%20lost%20or%20delayed%20baggage%2C%20travel%20delays%2C%20missed%20connections%2C%20trip%20cancellations%20and%20interruptions%20and%20more.%20You%20can%20even%20purchase%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpersonal-finance%2Ftravel-insurance%2Fcancel-for-any-reason-travel-insurance%5C%22%3Ecancel%20for%20any%20reason%20coverage%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20lets%20you%20cancel%20your%20trip%20and%20get%20a%20percentage%20of%20prepaid%20travel%20expenses%20back%20no%20matter%20the%20reason%20you%20can't%20go.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EChristina%20Schlegel%2C%20a%20travel%20agent%20with%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bluetailtravel.com%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EBluetail%20Travel%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20says%20you'll%20also%20want%20to%20have%20emergency%20medical%20evacuation%20coverage%20in%20place%20before%20a%20trip.%20This%20kind%20of%20coverage%20can%20pay%20for%20emergency%20transportation%20in%20an%20ambulance%2C%20a%20plane%20or%20a%20helicopter%20if%20you're%20injured%20and