re%20never%20in%20favour%20of%20having%20an%20all-India%20exam%20but%20were%20persuaded%20by%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%2C%20who%20was%20then%20the%20Chief%20Minister%20of%20Gujarat.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhen%20the%20exams%20were%20handed%20over%20to%20the%20Centre%20in%20brazen%20step%20of%20dismantling%20the%20federal%20structure%2C%20there%20were%20protests%20from%20our%20side%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Basu%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20then%20Chief%20Minister%20of%20Gujarat%20Narendra%20Modi%20had%20said%20that%20NEET%20exams%20should%20not%20be%20handled%20by%20the%20Centre%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThose%20who%20are%20bringing%20this%20resolution%20are%20neck%20deep%20in%20corruption%20in%20the%20education%20system.%20Trinamool%20and%20transparency%20have%20no%20connection%20at%20all%2C%26quot%3B%20countered%20state%20BJP's%20Sankar%20Ghosh.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20state's%20move%20came%20a%20day%20after%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20said%20there%20would%20be%20no%20re-test%20for%20NEET%2C%20since%20it%20was%20not%20conclusively%20proved%20that%20the%20sanctity%20of%20the%20exam%20has%20been%20breached.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20students%20who%20got%20question%20number%2029%20of%20the%20Physics%20paper%20wrong%2C%20will%20lose%20marks.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThere%20being%20two%20possible%20answers%20to%20the%20question%2C%20the%20ones%20who%20gave%20the%20second%20answer%20were%20also%20given%20marks.%20But%20under%20the%20entrance%20exam%20rules%2C%20a%20wrong%20answer%20leads%20to%20deduction%20of%20marks.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFollowing%20a%20petition%20by%20a%20student%2C%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20has%20also%20ruled%20that%20only%20one%20correct%20answer%20from%20a%20set%20of%20four%20answers%20will%20be%20valid.%20Following%20the%20court's%20decision%2C%20four%20lakh%20students%20will%20lose%20marks.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1721817600000%2C%22visual%22%3