2%3A%22%3Cp%3EBihar%2C%20one%20of%20the%20epicentres%20of%20several%20paper%20leaks%2C%20including%20that%20of%20the%20NEET-UG%20test%2C%20has%20passed%20a%20stringent%20bill%20to%20curb%20malpractices%20in%20government%20exams.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Bihar%20Public%20Examinations%20(PE)%20(Prevention%20of%20Unfair%20Means)%20Bill%2C%202024%2C%20was%20tabled%20by%20state%20Parliamentary%20Affairs%20Minister%20Vijay%20Kumar%20Chaudhary%20on%20Wednesday%20and%20passed%20with%20a%20voice%20vote%20amid%20a%20walkout%20by%20the%20opposition.%20The%20walkout%20was%20to%20protest%20lawlessness%20and%20the%20denial%20of%20special%20status%20to%20Bihar.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Bill%2C%20which%20had%20first%20been%20introduced%20in%20the%20monsoon%20session%2C%20has%20strict%20provisions%2C%20including%20a%20prison%20term%20of%20up%20to%2010%20years%20and%20a%20fine%20of%20Rs%201%20crore%20for%20those%20found%20guilty%20of%20involvement%20in%20irregularities%20in%20exams%20for%20both%20individuals%20and%20organisations.%20It%20also%20has%20a%20clause%20for%20attaching%20the%20properties%20of%20those%20found%20guilty%20and%20makes%20it%20difficult%20for%20people%20arrested%20for%20exam%20irregularities%20to%20get%20bail.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20passing%20its%20order%20on%20Tuesday%20in%20which%20it%20said%20there%20would%20be%20no%20retest%20for%20NEET-UG%2C%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20bench%20led%20by%20Chief%20Justice%20DY%20Chandrachud%20had%20also%20noted%20that%20the%20paper%20for%20the%20exam%20had%20been%20leaked%20for%20at%20least%20two%20centres%2C%20in%20Bihar's%20Patna%20and%20Hazaribagh%20in%20Jharkhand.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBihar%20has%20seen%20several%20paper%20leaks%20for%20state-level%20tests%20and%20gangs%20from%20the%20state%20have%20also%20been%20found%20involved%20in%20leaking%20papers%20or%20tampering%20with%20the%20examination%20process%20for%20national%20entrance%20exams.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20state's%20paper%20lea