er%20positions%20in%20her%20life.%20We%20priests%20offer%20special%20prayers%20for%20Usha%20and%20her%20husband.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EUsha's%20great-grandfather%20moved%20out%20of%20Vadluru%2C%20but%20her%20ancestors%20are%20respected%20in%20the%20village%20as%20academic%20highflyers%20and%20well-versed%20in%20Hindu%20scriptures.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHer%20father%20Chilukuri%20Radhakrishnan%20--%20a%20PhD%20holder%20--%20was%20brought%20up%20in%20Chennai%20and%20went%20on%20to%20study%20in%20the%20United%20States.%20He%20returned%20to%20India%20before%20the%20couple%20moved%20back%20across%20the%20Pacific%2C%20and%20Usha%20was%20brought%20up%20in%20suburban%20San%20Diego.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShe%20met%20Vance%20at%20Yale%20Law%20School%20and%20the%20couple%20married%20in%202014.%20They%20have%20three%20children.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3EHillbilly%20Elegy%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EUsha%20Vance%20has%20never%20visited%20the%20village%2C%20but%20the%20priest%20said%20her%20father%20last%20came%20around%20three%20years%20ago%20and%20checked%20on%20temple's%20condition.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELittle%20is%20known%20about%20Radhakrishnan's%20initial%20years%20in%20the%20United%20States%2C%20but%20the%20film%20of%20Vance's%20memoirs%2C%20Hillbilly%20Elegy%2C%20refers%20to%20him%20coming%20to%20the%20country%20with%20%26quot%3Bnothing%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EUsha's%20character%2C%20played%20by%20Indian%20actor%20Freida%20Pinto%2C%20says%20in%20the%202020%20movie%20now%20streaming%20on%20Netflix%20that%20her%20father%20had%20to%20%26quot%3Bfind%20his%20way%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EUsha%20is%20a%20practising%20Hindu%20and%20told%20Fox%20News%20in%20a%20recent%20interview%20that%20the%20faith%20made%20her%20mother%20and%20father%20%26quot%3Bgood%20parents...%20really%20good%20people%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHouses%20in%20Vadluru%20have%20%26quot%3BJai%20Sri%20Ram%26quot%3B%20--%20%26quot%3BVictory%20to%20Lord%20Ram%26quot%3B%20written%20in%20red%20on%20their%20walls.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EVillagers%20now%20follow%20the%20couple's%20campaign%20on%20Youtube%20and%20Facebook%2C%20said%20resident%20Venkata%20Ramanayya%2C%2070.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20feel%20very%20happy%20and%20proud%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3EUS%20migration%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMillions%20of%20Indians%20have%20made%20similar%20journeys%20as%20the%20Chilukuris%2C%20and%20according%20to%20the%20most%20recent%20US%20census%2C%20Indians%20have%20become%20the%20country's%20second-largest%20Asian%20ethnicity%2C%20growing%2050%20percent%20to%204.8%20million%20in%20the%20decade%20to%202020.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETrump's%20opponent%20in%20the%20November%20election%20is%20Kamala%20Harris%2C%20whose%20maternal%20grandfather%20hailed%20from%20Thulasendrapuram%2C%20a%20village%20surrounded%20by%20paddy%20fields%20deep%20in%20the%20southern%20state%20of%20Tamil%20Nadu.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHarris'%20maternal%20grandfather%20PV%20Gopalan%20left%20the%20village%20decades%20ago%2C%20but%20residents%20say%20the%20family%20has%20maintained%20close%20links%20and%20has%20regularly%20donated%20to%20the%20village%20temple's%20upkeep.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAround%20600%20kilometres%20away%20from%20Vadluru%2C%20Usha's%20great-grandaunt%20Chilukuri%20Santhamma%20sat%20hunched%20over%20a%20pile%20of%20papers%20as%20she%20called%20on%20her%20relative%20to%20urge%20others%20not%20to%20follow%20in%20her%20family's%20footsteps.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnother%20of%20the%20family%20academics%2C%20at%2096%20she%20is%20hailed%20in%20local%20media%20as%20the%20country's%20oldest%20active%20professor.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShe%20is%20related%20to%20Usha%20through%20her%20husband%2C%20an%20academic%20himself%20who%20was%20associated%20with%20the%20Rashtriya%20Swayamsevak%20Sangh%20(RSS).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EUsha%20should%20use%20her%20position%20and%20legal%20knowledge%20to%20stop%20the%20%26quot%3Bdrain%26quot%3B%20of%20Indians%20into%20the%20United%20States%2C%20Santhamma%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThey%20can%20go%20for%20education%2C%20they%20can%20go%20for%20training%2C%20all%20this%20they%20can%20do%20but%20there%20is%20a%20limitation.%20They%20have%20to%20stay%20there%20for%20known%20time%20and%20come%20back%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShe%20believes%20Usha%20has%20a%20tough%20life%2C%20despite%20being%20married%20to%20a%20%26quot%3Bgreat%20person%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BTo%20become%20the%20wife%20of%20a%20great%20person%20is%20the%20fortune%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said%2C%20but%20has%20%26quot%3Btaken%20politics%20as%20her%20subject%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThat%20is%20a%20very%20tough%20one%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1721813520000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-07%2F6e2p4ghg_usha-vance-andhra_625x300_24_July_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fwhy-this-andhra-village-is-praying-for-us-vice-presidential-candidate-jd-vances-wife-6177651%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Every%20day%20in%20a%20simple%20temple%20in%20an%20Andhra%20Pradesh%20village%2C%20Hindu%20priest%20Subhramanya%20Sharma%20prays%20for%20JD%20Vance%20to%20become%20vice-president%20of%20the%20United%20States.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fwhy-this-andhra-village-is-praying-for-us-vice-presidential-candidate-jd-vances-wife-6177651%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fwhy-this-andhra-village-is-praying-for-us-vice-presidential-candidate-jd-vances-wife-6177651%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fwhy-this-andhra-village-is-praying-for-us-vice-preside