t%3D%5C%22Add%20image%20caption%20here%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22Add%20image%20caption%20here%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-07%2F3i2bn6og_budget_625x300_24_July_24.jpg%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20deft%20move%2C%20the%20Narendra%20Modi%20government%20on%20Tuesday%20managed%20to%20strike%20a%20balance%20as%20it%20announced%20a%20liberal%20allocation%20for%20Bihar%20in%20the%20Union%20Budget%20without%20yielding%20ground%20on%20the%20state's%20demand%20for%20a%20'special'%20status%20or%20package.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShowing%20political%20dexterity%2C%20Union%20Finance%20Minister%20Nirmala%20Sitharaman%20announced%20that%20the%20Budget%20proposes%20to%20support%20several%20standalone%20infrastructure%20projects%20in%20the%20state.%20Under%20this%2C%20Rs%2026%2C000%20crore%20will%20be%20allocated%20for%20developing%20four%20specific%20road%20projects%2C%20Rs%2021%2C400%20crore%20is%20earmarked%20for%20power%20projects%2C%20including%20a%20new%202%2C400%20MW%20plant%20at%20Pirpainti%2C%20and%20Rs%2011%2C500%20crore%20has%20been%20set%20aside%20for%20flood%20management.%20New%20airports%2C%20medical%20colleges%20and%20sports%20infrastructure%20in%20the%20state%20were%20part%20of%20the%20promises.%20Sitharaman%20also%20said%20additional%20allocation%20would%20be%20made%20to%20support%20capital%20investments%20and%20that%20the%20Centre%20would%20expedite%20the%20requests%20of%20the%20Bihar%20Government%20for%20external%20assistance%20from%20multilateral%20development%20banks.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EMutual%20Dependence%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Janata%20Dal%20(United)%20(JD-U)%20was%20swift%20to%20appreciate%20the%20package%2C%20with%20Chief%20Minister%20Nitish%20Kumar%20stating%20that%20though%20he%20had%20initially%20been%20pressing%20for%20special%20status%20for%20Bihar%2C%20the%20state%20has%20now%20got%20special%20aid.%20JD(U)%20spokesperson%20K.C.%20Tyagi%20estimated%20the%20allocations%20would%20touch%20Rs.%201%20Lakh%20crore%2C%20which%20will%20go%20a%20long%20way%20in%20building%20an%20'Atmanirbhar'%20Bihar.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBihar%20is%20headed%20for%20assembly%20polls%20next%20year%2C%20and%20thus%2C%20the%20stakes%20are%20high%20for%20the%20National%20Democratic%20Alliance%20(NDA)%20in%20the%20state%2C%20which%20depends%20on%20Nitish%20Kumar%20and%20Andhra%20Pradesh%20Chief%20Minister%20Chandrababu%20Naidu%20to%20retain%20power%20at%20the%20Centre.%20The%20JD(U)%20has%20held%20the%20reins%20in%20Bihar%20for%20two%20decades%20now%2C%20with%20relations%20with%20the%20BJP%20changing%20frequently.%20Nitish%2C%20who%20goes%20by%20the%20name%20'Sushashan%20Babu'%20in%20his%20home%20state%2C%20is%20aware%20that%20he%20will%20be%20under%20intense%20scrutiny%20by%20both%20the%20Rashtriya%20Janata%20Dal%20(RJD)-led%20opposition%20front%20and%20the%20BJP.%20The%20latter%20would%20like%20to%20occupy%20prime%20political%20space%20in%20Bihar%20in%20the%20long%20run.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20for%20now%2C%20the%20Bharatiya%20Janata%20Party%20(BJP)-led%20NDA%20has%20taken%20a%20pragmatic%20approach%20as%20it%20humours%20a%20leader%20known%20for%20his%20political%20flip-flops.%20In%20a%20way%2C%20the%20dependence%20is%20mutual.%20While%20the%20BJP%20needs%20the%20JD(U)%20at%20the%20Centre%2C%20Nitish%20needs%20to%20prove%20to%20his%20electorate%20that%20his%20prime%20objective%2C%20irrespective%20of%20his%20political%20flip-flops%2C%20is%20to%20secure%20the%20best%20deal%20for%20Bihar.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhat%20The%20Bihar%20Package%20Includes%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20aforementioned%20allocations%20for%20Bihar%20are%20in%20addition%20to%20plans%20for%20supporting%20the%20development%20of%20an%20industrial%20node%20at%20Gaya%20as%20part%20of%20the%20Amritsar-Kolkata%20Industrial%20Corridor.%20The%20idea%20to%20develop%20the%20node%20at%20Gaya%2C%20Sitharaman%20said%2C%20was%20centred%20around%20the%20motto%20%26quot%3B%3Cem%3EVikas%20bhi%20Virasat%20bhi%3C%2Fem%3E%26quot%3B%2C%20that%20is%2C%20development%20around%20heritage.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBihar%20has%20also%20been%20made%20part%20of%20a%20grand%20'Purvodaya%26quot%3B%20plan%2C%20which%20covers%20Jharkhand%2C%20West%20Bengal%2C%20Odisha%20and%20Andhra%20Pradesh%20and%20aims%20to%20push%20all-round%20development%20of%20the%20eastern%20region.%20Human%20resource%20and%20infrastructural%20development%20as%20well%20as%20the%20generation%20of%20economic%20opportunities%20are%20the%20key%20goals%20of%20the%20programme.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20road%20projects%20announced%20include%20the%20Patna-Purnea%20Expressway%2C%20the%20Buxar-Bhagalpur%20Expressway%2C%20Bodhgaya%2C%20Rajgir%2C%20Vaishali%20and%20Darbhanga%20spurs%2C%20and%20an%20additional%20two-lane%20bridge%20over%20river%20Ganga%20at%20Buxar.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFurther%2C%20in%20order%20to%20mitigate%20the%20perennial%20problem%20of%20floods%20that%20ravage%20the%20state%20every%20year%2C%20the%20Budget%20states%20that%20plans%20to%20build%20flood%20control%20infrastructures%20in%20Nepal%20are%20yet%20to%20progress.%20Also%2C%20the%20government%20will%20provide%20financial%20support%20to%20the%20tune%20of%20Rs.%2011%2C500%20crore%20for%20projects%20under%20the%20Accelerated%20Irrigation%20Benefit%20Programme%20and%20other%20sources.%20These%20cover%20the%20Kosi-Mechi%20intra-state%20link%20and%2020%20other%20ongoing%20and%20new%20projects%2C%20which%20include%20barrages%2C%20river%20pollution%20abatement%20projects%2C%20and%20irrigation%20links.%20The%20plan%20also%20envisages%20undertaking%20a%20survey%20and%20investigation%20of%20Kosi-related%20flood%20mitigation%20and%20irrigation%20projects.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBetween%20now%20and%20the%20elections%2C%20the%20focus%20will%20be%20to%20translate%20these%20big%20announcements%20into%20a%20reality%20for%20the%20people%20of%20Bihar.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E(K.V.%20Prasad%20is%20a%20senior%20Delhi-based%20journalist)%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EDisclaimer%3A%20These%20are%20the%20personal%20opinions%20of%20the%20author%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1721813100000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-07%2Feavsu0lo_budget_625x300_24_July_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fopinion%2Fbudget-2024-has-big-promises-for-bihar-even-if-no-special-status-6177323%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22In%20a%20deft%20move%2C%20the%20Narendra%20Modi%20government%20on%20Tuesday%20managed%20to%20strike%20a%20balance%20as%20it%20announced%20a%20liberal%20allocation%20for%20Bihar%20in%20the%20Union%20Budget%20without%20yielding%20ground%20on%20the%20state's%20demand%20for%20a%20'special%20status%2Fpackage'.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fopinion%2Fbudget-2024-has-big-promises-for-bihar-even-if-no-special-status-6177323%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Bodycam%20footage%20shows%20moments%20after%20man%20who%20tried%20to%20assassinate%20Trump%20was%20shot%20dead%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1721812680000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fe3.365dm.com%2F24%2F07%2F1920x1080%2Fskynews-crooks-thomas_6637785.jpg%3F20240724120152%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fnews.sky.com%2Fstory%2Fbodycam-footage-shows-moments-after-man-who-tried-to-assassinate-donald-trump-was-shot-dead-13184144%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Bodycam%20footage%20shows%20law%20enforcement%20officers%20gathered%20near%20the%20body%20of%20the%20man%20who%20was%20shot%20dead%20after%20trying%20to%20assassinate%20Donald%20Trump.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fnews.sky.com%2Fstory%2Fbodycam-footage-shows-moments-after-man-who-tried-to-assassinate-donald-trump-was-shot-dead-13184144%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22%26quot%3BWill%20March%20To%20