below.%20Nineteen%20passengers%20and%20both%20pilots%20died%2C%20but%20169%20others%20survived.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECivil%20Aviation%20regulator%2C%20Directorate%20General%20of%20Civil%20Aviation%2C%20holds%20periodical%20reviews%20of%20table-top%20airports%20to%20ensure%20passenger%20safety.%20Back%20in%202022%2C%20an%20official%20of%20the%20DGCA%20had%20told%20the%20media%20that%20the%20objective%20behind%20the%20review%20was%20to%20prevent%20any%20unforeseen%20incidents%20and%20look%20for%20ways%20to%20make%20landings%20in%20these%20airports%20less%20challenging.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPortugal's%20Madeira%20airport%2C%20which%20has%20a%20table-top%20runway%2C%20reported%20a%20crash%20back%20in%201977%20when%20an%20Air%20Portugal%20Flight%20425%20overshot%20and%20crashed%20onto%20a%20beach%2C%20killing%20131%20people.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEven%20Nepal%2C%20which%20has%20a%20poor%20air%20travel%20safety%20record%2C%20has%20reported%20crashes%20involving%20table-top%20runways%20in%20the%20past.%20On%20May%2027%2C%202017%2C%20a%20cargo%20plane%20at%20crashed%20at%20the%20Tenzing-Hillary%20airport%20in%20Solukhumbu%2C%20which%20has%20such%20a%20runway.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20crash%20that%20took%20place%20this%20morning%2C%20the%20Bombardier%20CRJ%20200%20flight%20skidded%20off%20the%20runway%20and%20burst%20into%20flames%2C%20a%20spokesperson%20of%20the%20airport%20has%20told%20NDTV.%20Tribhuvan%20airport%20in%20Kathmandu%2C%20where%20the%20crash%20took%20place%2C%20is%20on%20the%20top%20of%20a%20plateau%20and%20is%20surrounded%20by%20deep%20gorges%20and%20valleys%20on%20all%20sides.%20Kathmandu%20airport%20is%20among%20the%20most%20risky%20airports%20to%20land%20and%20was%20the%20site%20of%20a%20huge%20crash%20back%20in%201992%2C%20when%20167%20passengers%20of%20a%20Pakistan%20International%20Airlines%20plane%20had%20died.%20The%20Saurya%20Airlines%20flight%20that%20crashed%20today%20had%20crew%20and%20technical%20staff%20on%20board%20and%20was%20on%20its%20way%