he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20minister%20cited%20the%20example%20of%20Maharashtra%2C%20which%20did%20not%20find%20a%20mention%20in%20her%20budget%20speech%20on%20February%201%20or%20yesterday.%20%26quot%3BThe%20cabinet%20has%2C%20under%20the%20leadership%20of%20Prime%20Minister%20(Narendra)%20Modi%2C%20taken%20the%20decision%20to%20set%20up%20a%20very%20big%20port%20in%20Vadhavan%20in%20Maharashtra.%20Did%20Maharashtra%20get%20ignored%20because%20I%20did%20not%20mention%20the%20name%3F%20Rs%2076%2C000%20crore%20have%20been%20announced%20for%20that%20project.%26quot%3B%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIf%20the%20speech%20does%20not%20mention%20a%20particular%20state%2C%20does%20it%20mean%20the%20schemes%20of%20the%20government%20of%20India%2C%20the%20programmes%20of%20the%20government%20of%20India%2C%20the%20external%20aided%20assistance%20we%20obtain%20don't%20go%20to%20these%20states%3F%26quot%3B%20she%20asked.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShe%20alleged%20that%20this%20is%20a%20deliberate%20attempt%20by%20the%20Opposition%20led%20by%20the%20Congress%20to%20give%20an%20impression%20to%20people%20that%20nothing%20is%20being%20given%20to%20states%20ruled%20by%20non-NDA%20parties.%20%26quot%3BI%20would%20challenge%20the%20Congress%20party%2C%20in%20each%20of%20their%20budget%20speeches%2C%20have%20they%20named%20every%20state%20of%20this%20country.%20This%20is%20an%20outrageous%20allegation%2C%26quot%3B%20Ms%20Sitharaman%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20some%20members%20of%20the%20Trinamool%20Congress%20returned%20to%20the%20House%2C%20the%20Finance%20Minister%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BYesterday%2C%20the%20TMC%20questioned%20the%20Budget%2C%20saying%20nothing%20has%20been%20given%20to%20Bengal.%20Let%20me%20highlight%20the%20fact%20that%20several%20schemes%20given%20by%20the%20Prime%20Minister%20in%20the%20last%2010%20years%20have%20not%20even%20been%20implemented%20in%20West%20Bengal.%20And%20you%20have%20the%20audacity%20to%20ask%20me%20now%3F%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETrinamool%20members%20hit%20back%2C%20pointing%20at%20the%20unpaid%20dues%20the%20Centre%20owes%20to%20Bengal.%20Party%20MP%20Mausam%20Noor%20raised%20the%20issue%20of%20floods%20in%20north%20Bengal's%20Malda.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20Finance%20Minister%20has%20not%20been%20generous%20at%20all.%20Zero%20has%20been%20given%20to%20Bengal%20and%20zero%20has%20been%20given%20to%20battle%20the%20floods%20in%20Malda.%20Every%20monsoon%2C%20Malda%20is%20devastated%20by%20floods%20in%20Ganga%2C%20Mahananda%2C%20Pulahar%20and%20Tangan.%20This%20year%2C%20it's%20more%20alarming.%20Over%20the%20course%20of%20time%2C%20the%20rivers%20have%20changed%20their%20directions%20and%20the%20distance%20between%20Ganga%20and%20Pulahar%20has%20come%20down%20to%20only%20700%20metres.%20If%20these%20rivers%20merge%2C%20there%20will%20be%20a%20huge%20disaster%2C%20causing%20colossal%20damage.%20Huge%20areas%20will%20be%20engulfed.%20People%20will%20lose%20land%2C%20mango%20orchards%2C%20farming%20fields%20and%20the%20situation%20will%20render%20lakhs%20homeless%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMs%20Noor%20said%20that%20the%20issue%20comes%20under%20the%20Centre's%20purview%20and%20Chief%20Minister%20Mamata%20Banerjee%20has%20asked%20the%20Water%20Resources%20Ministry%20and%20the%20Farakka%20Barrage%20authorities%20several%20times%20to%20come%20up%20with%20a%20permanent%20solution.%20%26quot%3BDuring%20the%20UPA%20regime%2C%20anti-erosion%20and%20bank%20protection%20work%20had%20been%20conducted%20several%20times.%20But%20since%202014%2C%20Farakka%20Barrage%20has%20failed%20to%20combat%20the%20situation%20and%20take%20any%20major%20action%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said%2C%20seeking%20immediate%20attention%20to%20this%20issue.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECriticising%20the%20government%20over%20the%20Budget%2C%20Congress%20president%20Kharge%20has%20said%20the%20budget%20is%20a%20fraud%20against%20the%20people%20of%20the%20country.%20%26quot%3BNo%20state%20got%20anything%2C%20ev