0laugh%20about%20her%20pot%20of%20%26quot%3Bsteaming%20hot%20water%2C%26quot%3B%20before%20she%20says%20twice%2C%20%26quot%3BI%20rebuke%20you%20in%20the%20name%20of%20Jesus.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BYou%20better%20not%2C%20or%20I%20swear%20to%20God%20I'll%20shoot%20you%20in%20your%20%5Bexpletive%5D%20face%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr.%20Grayson%20responds%2C%20drawing%20his%20pistol%20and%20shouting%20for%20her%20to%20drop%20the%20pot.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20data-media-max-width%3D%5C%22560%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22twitter-tweet%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%20lang%3D%5C%22en%5C%22%3EGRAPHIC%20VIDEO%20%7C%20Officials%20release%20video%20of%20officer%20fatally%20shooting%2026-year-old%20Sonya%20Massey%20in%20her%20home%20after%20she%20called%20911%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cbr%3E%5CnSonya%20Massey%20was%20shot%20in%20the%20face%20by%20Sangamon%20County%20Sheriff's%20Deputy%20Sean%20Grayson.%20Grayson%2C%20who%20pleaded%20not%20guilty%20to%20first-degree%20murder%20and%20other%E2%80%A6%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ft.co%2Fc5xkBzwJOm%5C%22%3Epic.twitter.com%2Fc5xkBzwJOm%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%E2%80%94%20Bobby%20Ellison%20(%40BobbyEllisonKY)%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FBobbyEllisonKY%2Fstatus%2F1815849976507076978%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3EJuly%2023%2C%202024%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20statement%2C%20President%20Biden%20expressed%20being%20%26quot%3Bheartbroken%26quot%3B%20for%20her%20family%20and%20noted%20that%20her%20death%20serves%20as%20a%20reminder%20%26quot%3Bthat%20all%20too%20often%20Black%20Americans%20face%20fears%20for%20their%20safety%20in%20ways%20many%20of%20the%20rest%20of%20us%20do%20not.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EVice-President%20Kamala%20Harris%20called%20on%20Congress%20to%20pass%20police%20reforms%2C%20stating%20on%20X%3A%20%26quot%3BSonya%20Massey%20deserved%20to%20be%20safe.%20The%20disturbing%20footage%20released%20yesterday%20confirms