e%20plants%20that%20thrive%20in%20limited%20sunlight%2C%20as%20a%20large%20tree%20already%20shades%20the%20area.%20He%20opted%20for%20seasonal%20flowers%20and%20ornamental%20plants%2C%20intentionally%20avoiding%20species%20commonly%20used%20in%20religious%20practices%20to%20discourage%20plucking.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERemarkably%2C%20this%20roadside%20garden%E2%80%99s%20beauty%20is%20a%20collective%20effort.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EManoj%E2%80%99s%20family%2C%20including%20his%20two%20daughters%2C%20Ananya%20and%20Manisha%20Dubey%2C%20have%20actively%20helped%20flourish%20the%20garden.%20They%20decorate%20the%20space%20with%20colourful%20bricks%20and%20creatively%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F356071%2Fhow-to-grow-plants-in-recycled-plastic-containers-old-bottles-urban-gardeners-share-tips%2F%23google_vignette%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Erecycled%20pots.%3C%2Fa%3E%20His%20initiative%20has%20inspired%20neighbours%2C%20sparking%20a%20trend%20of%20roadside%20gardens%20throughout%20the%20community.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EManoj%E2%80%99s%20garden%20has%20also%20become%20a%20local%20attraction%2C%20with%20people%20passing%20by%20just%20to%20enjoy%20the%20view.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhat%20started%20as%20a%20personal%20passion%20project%20has%20become%20a%20community%20highlight.%20This%20showcases%20how%20urban%20spaces%20can%20be%20converted%20into%20lush%20gardens%20and%20proves%20that%20anyone%20can%20contribute%20to%20beautifying%20their%20surroundings%2C%20regardless%20of%20space%20constraints.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFollowing%20his%20lead%2C%20you%20too%20can%20transform%20vacant%20spaces%20around%20your%20house%20into%20thriving%20gardens%20and%20contribute%20to%20beautifying%20your%20city.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHappy%20gardening!%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EEdited%20by%20Khushi%20Arora.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1721800949000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2F