erstand%20the%20importance%20of%20ODR.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20have%20started%20sending%20offline%20notices%20to%20parties%20and%20making%20sure%20that%20the%20experience%20for%20our%203%2C000%20lawyers%20is%20good%20so%20that%20they%20can%20spread%20the%20word%20about%20ODR.%20We%20are%20also%20experimenting%20with%20artificial%20intelligence%20to%20handle%20more%20case%20volume%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20shares.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2Fsama-1721374378.jpg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Sama%20was%20featured%20in%20the%20Shark%20Tank%20India%20season%203%20and%20bagged%20a%20deal%20of%20Rs%201%20crore.%20%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2Fsama-1721374378.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2Fsama-1721374378-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2Fsama-1721374378-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2Fsama-1721374378-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2Fsama-1721374378-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-357646%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3ESama%20was%20recently%20featured%20in%20the%20Shark%20Tank%20India%20season%203%20and%20bagged%20a%20deal%20of%20Rs%201%20crore.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETo%20ensure%20speedy%20out%20of%20court%20settlements%2C%20Sama%20incentivises%20success%20rates%20of%20cases%20instead%20of%20paying%20fee%20per%20hearing.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CUsually%2C%20we%20see%20that%20lawyers%20try%20to%20extract%20more%20amounts%20from%20clients%20and%20keep%20delaying%20the%20case.%20But%20our%20business%20model%20is%20based%20on%20incentivising%20the%20lawyers%20based%20on%20the%20success%20rates%20of%20the%20cases.%20We%20give%204x%20money%20if%20the%20settlement%20is%20reached%20on%20time.%20This%20encourages%20mediators%20to%20solve%20the%20cases%20fast%20and%20reach%20a%20conclusion%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%20every%20case%2C%20Sama%20charges%20one%20percent%20of%20the%20claim%20amounts%20in%20the%20case.%20%E2%80%9CIf%20the%20dispute%20is%20within%20a%C2%A0%20lakh%2C%20we%20charge%20the%20client%20Rs%201%2C000%2C%20whereas%20we%20take%20Rs%202%2C000%20for%20clients%20between%20Rs%201-3%20lakh.%20This%20is%2099%20percent%20cheaper%20than%20the%20courts%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEarly%20this%20year%2C%20Sama%20was%20featured%20in%20the%20Shark%20Tank%20India%20season%203%20and%20bagged%20a%20deal%20of%20Rs%201%20crore%20from%20boAt%20co-founder%20Aman%20Gupta%2C%20Namita%20Thapar%2C%20the%20executive%20director%20of%20Emcure%20Pharmaceuticals%2C%20and%20Ritesh%20Agarwal%2C%20the%20CEO%20of%20OYO%20Rooms.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CNot%20only%20did%20we%20receive%20the%20funding%20but%20this%20exposure%20also%20helped%20us%20get%20a%20good%20reach%20and%20spread%20awareness%20about%20ODR.%20Our%20idea%20got%20a%20validation%20when%20we%20explained%20it%20to%20the%20viewers%20in%20a%20non-legal%20language.%20Finally%2C%20our%20families%20also%20understood%20what%20we%20were%20trying%20to%20do%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20laughs.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELooking%20at%20the%20success%20of%20the%20startup%2C%20Pranjal%20says%2C%20%E2%80%9CPersonally%2C%20it%20has%20been%20a%20very%20challenging%20but%20rewarding%20journey%20for%20us.%20I%20really%20feel%20Sama%20is%20a%20divine%20%3Cem%3Esewa%20%3C%2Fem%3E(service).%20Every%20day%2C%20we%20deal%20with%20a%20lot%20of%20negativity%20but%20when%20years%20long%20disputes%20are%20solved%2C%20we%20get%20equal%20amounts%20of%20satisfaction.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIt%20will%20take%20us%20another%2010%20years%20to%20make%20Sama%20a%20primary%20resort%20for%20civil%20disputes%20to%20be%20able%20to%20reduce%20the%20burden%20on%20courts%20so%20that%20they%20can%20focus%20on%20criminal%20cases%20instead%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EEdited%20by%20Padmashree%20Pande.%20All%20photos%3A%20Pranjal%20Sinha.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1721390593000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2Fsama-2-1721374464.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F%3Fp%3D357644%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Pranjal%20Sinha%2C%20Akshetha%20Ashok%2C%20and%20Vikram%20Kumar%20started%20Sama%2C%20a%20legal%20startup%20working%20to%20reduce%20court%20load%20with%20fast%20and%20cost-effective%20resolution%20of%20civil%20disputes%20online.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22Shivani%20Gupta%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A29%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F357644%2Fsama-legal-tech-startup-resolves-civil-disputes-through-online-dispute-resolution-odr%2F%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22The%20Unexpected%20Origin%20Stories%20of%20Chicken%20Tikka%20Masala%20%26amp%3B%20a%20Must-Try%20Recipe%20by%20Chef%20Ranveer%20Brar%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EAnyone%20who%E2%80%99s%20on%20their%20early%20morning%20jog%20or%20a%20drive%20in%20South%20Manchester%2C%20England%20has%20more%20often%20than%20not%20had%20the%20feeling%20of%20having%20just%20been%20swallowed%20up%20by%20an%20inter-dimensional%20portal.%20This%20feeling%20peaks%20at%20Wilmslow%20Road%2C%20which%20runs%20through%20the%20centre%20of%20Rusholme.%20In%20an%20instant%2C%20the%20physical%20landscape%20of%20top-notch%2C%20stone-structure%2C%20Michelin-starred%20fine-dining%20restaurants%20with%20coiffured%20waiters%20gives%20way%20to%20sprightly%2C%20pop-up%20eateries%20with%20attractive%20hoardings.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWelcome%20to%20%E2%80%98The%20Curry%20Mile%E2%80%99%20%E2%80%94%20an%20area%20of%20England%20that%20is%20believed%20to%20have%20the%20largest%20concentration%20of%20South%20Asian%20restaurants%20in%20the%20United%20Kingdom.%20Since%20the%2050s%20%E2%80%94%20when%20this%20area%20became%20a%20boomtown%20of%20textile%20mills%20recruiting%20men%20from%20South%20Asia%20who%20went%20on%20to%20set%20up%20their%20restaurants%20here%20%E2%80%94%20Curry%20Mile%20has%20become%20synonymous%20with%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F356455%2Fbest-breakfast-places-in-new-delhi-shops-cafes-restaurants-chhole-bhature-pancakes-kachori%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EIndian%20food%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EKebabs%20%3C%2Fem%3E(minced%20meat%20cooked%20on%20skewers)%2C%20grills%2C%20%3Cem%3Eshawarma%20%3C%2Fem%3E(a%20Middle%20Eastern%20dish%20consisting%20of%20meat%20that%20is%20cut%20into%20thin%20slices%2C%20stacked%20in%20an%20inverted%20cone%2C%20and%20roasted%20on%20a%20slow-turning%20vertical%20spit)%2C%20%3Cem%3Egol%20gappas%3C%2Fem%3E%20(deep-fried%20breaded%20hollow%20spherical%20shell%20filled%20with%20a%20combination%20of%20finely%20diced%20potato%2C%20onion%2C%20peas%2C%20and%20chickpea)%20and%20%3Cem%3Etandoori%20%3C%2Fem%3Echicken%20(a%20dish%20made%20from%20chicken%20marinated%20in%20yoghurt%20and%20spices%20and%20roasted%20in%20a%20%3Cem%3Etandoor%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20a%20cylindrical%20clay%20oven)%20make%20up%20a%20major%20part%20of%20the%20area%E2%80%99s%20offerings.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBrilliant%20and%20unique%20though%20each%20menu%20is%20%E2%80%94%20a%20fact%20that%20owes%20to%20their%20owners%E2%80%99%20cultural%20roots%20in%20different%20parts%20of%20South%20Asia%20%E2%80%94%20the%20restaurants%20at%20Curry%20Mile%20are%20bound%20by%20a%20single%20promise%3A%20to%20serve%20you%20the%20best%20%3Cem%3Echicken%20tikka%20masala%3C%2Fem%3E.%20So%2C%20have%20a%20seat%20while%20we%20regale%20you%20with%20the%20vibrant%20(and%20debatable)%20origins%20of%20one%20of%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F326173%2Forigins-of-iconic-indian-dishes-loved-across-the-world-food-history%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ehistory%E2%80%99s%20most%20loved%20dishes%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20640px)%20100vw%2C%20640px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2F36869943_2009599892410608_4959226096185769984_n-1721034983.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22640%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20chicken%20tikka%20masala%20is%20a%20popular%20dish%20in%20both%2C%20India%20and%20the%20UK%2C%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2F36869943_2009599892410608_4959226096185769984_n-1721034983.jpg%20640w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2F36869943_2009599892410608_4959226096185769984_n-1721034983-300x240.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2F36869943_2009599892410608_4959226096185769984_n-1721034983-500x400.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2F36869943_2009599892410608_4959226096185769984_n-1721034983-150x120.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-356875%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22512%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EThe%20chicken%3Cem%3E%20tikka%20masala%3C%2Fem%3E%20is%20a%20popular%20dish%20in%20both%2C%20India%20and%20the%20UK%2C%20Picture%20source%3A%20Facebook%3A%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%20nofollow%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2FKhanaIndianforFood%2Fposts%2Fchicken-tikka-masala-our-signature-dish-with-no-sugar-and-made-from-free-range-c%2F2009602082410389%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EKhana-Indian%20for%20Food%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EA%20very%20saucy%20mystery%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFew%20topics%20in%20history%20have%20conjured%20up%20as%20much%20debate%20as%20have%20a%20bunch%20of%20boneless%20pieces%20of%20chicken%2C%20marinated%20in%20spices%20and%20yoghurt%2C%20cooked%20in%20a%20%3Cem%3Etandoor%2C%20%3C%2Fem%3Ebrushed%20with%20%3Cem%3Eghee%20%3C%2Fem%3Eand%20served%20in%20a%20smooth%20tomato-cream%20sauce.%20Food%20aficionados%2C%20governments%2C%20historians%20and%20the%20people%20of%20Britain%20and%20India%20have%20constantly%20been%20engaged%20in%20a%20tug-of-war%20to%20dispute%20the%20origins%20of%20the%3Cem%3E%20%3C%2Fem%3Echicken%20%3Cem%3Etikka%20masala%3C%2Fem%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20milder%20take%20on%20this%2C%20as%20someone%20neutral%20to%20the%20argument%2C%20would%20suggest%20is%20that%20the%20gravy%20is%20a%20cross-fertilisation%20of%20ideas%20and%20a%20genius%20of%20many%20minds.%20Today%2C%20we%20explore%20this%20diplomatic%20stance%2C%20while%20also%20hearing%20out%20what%20each%20side%20has%20to%20say%20about%20the%20%3Cem%3Etikka%3C%2Fem%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20most%20accepted%20story%20is%20also%20the%20most%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F251933%2Fsakshi-deepa-guha-bengali-love-cafe-mother-daughter-gurugram-food-startup-authentic-homemade-bengali-food-tiffin-services-zomato-swiggy-him16%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eculturally%20vibrant%20%3C%2Fa%3Eone.%20It%20involves%20a%20%3Cem%3EBangladeshi%3C%2Fem%3E%20chef%20at%20a%20Scottish%20restaurant%20and%20(multiple%20sources%20suggest%20different%20professions)%20a%20hungry%20bus%20driver.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOne%20rainy%20day%20in%201971%2C%20Chef%20Ali%20Ahmed%20Aslam%20cooked%20up%20a%20dish%20(chicken%20%3Cem%3Etikka%3C%2Fem%3E)%20for%20a%20customer%20who%20stopped%20by%20the%20Shish%20Mahal%20restaurant%20in%20Glasgow%2C%20Scotland.%20The%20customer%20did%20not%20seem%20too%20appeased%20by%20the%20order%20and%20sent%20it%20back%20to%20the%20kitchens%20terming%20it%20%E2%80%9Ctoo%20dry%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EChannelling%20his%20curatorial%20skills%2C%20Chef%20Ali%20decided%20to%20make%20up%20for%20the%20dish%E2%80%99s%20lacking%20moisture%20with%20a%20creamy%20tomato%20soup.%20This%20seemed%20to%20satisfy%20the%20bus%20driver%20who%20turned%20into%20a%20loyal%20customer%20at%20the%20Shish%20Mahal%20and%20made%20it%20a%20point%20to%20order%20the%20dish%20on%20each%20visit.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20data-instgrm-captioned%20data-instgrm-version%3D%5C%2214%5C%22%20data-instgrm-permalink%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fp%2FBgRvOdmhvs-%2F%3Futm_source%3Dig_embed%26amp%3Butm_campaign%3Dloading%5C%22%3E%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fp%2FBgRvOdmhvs-%2F%3Futm_source%3Dig_embed%26utm_campaign%3Dloading%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3EView%20this%20post%20on%20Instagram%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fp%2FBgRvOdmhvs-%2F%3Futm_source%3Dig_embed%26utm_campaign%3Dloading%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EA%20post%20shared%20by%20Shish%20Mahal%20(%40officialshishmahal)%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%20%5Cn%3Cp%3EMeanwhile%2C%20the%20name%20and%20fame%20of%20the%20chicken%20%3Cem%3Etikka%20masala%3C%2Fem%3E%20spread%20far%20and%20wide%2C%20and%20restaurants%20in%20England%20were%20quick%20to%20clone%20the%20idea%2C%20furthering%20its%20legacy.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EChef%20Ali%20passed%20in%202022%20at%20the%20age%20of%2077%2C%20but%20not%20before%20he%20gave%20multiple%20interviews%20that%20were%20all%20aimed%20at%20finding%20out%20where%20the%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F309836%2Ffood-history-of-idli-sambar-roots-in-indonesia-south-indian-breakfast%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eorigins%20of%20the%20dish%3C%2Fa%3E%20truly%20lie.%20In%20one%20of%20his%20interviews%20with%20AFP%2C%20Ali%20seconded%20the%20theory%20that%20the%20%3Cem%3Etikka%20%3C%2Fem%3Ewas%20his%20creation.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CChicken%20%3Cem%3Etikka%20masala%20%3C%2Fem%3Ewas%20invented%20in%20this%20%5BShish%20Mahal%5D%20restaurant.%20We%20used%20to%20make%20%3Cem%3Echicken%20tikka%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20and%20one%20day%20a%20customer%20said%2C%20%E2%80%98I%E2%80%99d%20take%20some%20sauce%20with%20that%2C%20this%20is%20a%20bit%20dry%E2%80%99.%20We%20thought%20we%E2%80%99d%20better%20cook%20the%20chicken%20with%20some%20sauce.%20So%20from%20here%2C%20we%20cooked%20chicken%20%3Cem%3Etikka%20%3C%2Fem%3Ewith%20a%20sauce%20that%20contains%20yoghurt%2C%20cream%2C%20and%20spices.%20It%E2%80%99s%20a%20dish%20prepared%20according%20to%20our%20customer%E2%80%99s%20taste.%20Usually%2C%20they%20don%E2%80%99t%20take%20hot%20curry%20%E2%80%93%20that%E2%80%99s%20why%20we%20cook%20it%20with%20yoghurt%20and%20cream.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EWho%20is%20taking%20the%20prize%20home%3F%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhat%20really%20set%20the%20stage%20for%20debate%2C%20was%20a%20speech%20made%20in%202001%20by%20the%20then-British%20foreign%20secretary%20Robin%20Cook%20who%20hailed%20the%20chicken%20%3Cem%3Etikka%20masala%3C%2Fem%3E%20as%20a%20%E2%80%9Ctrue%20British%20national%20dish%E2%80%9D.%20Indians%20weren%E2%80%99t%20thrilled%20with%20this%20claim.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20Cook%20went%20on%2C%20%E2%80%9C%E2%80%A6not%20only%20because%20it%20is%20the%20most%20popular%2C%20but%20because%20it%20is%20a%20perfect%20illustration%20of%20the%20way%20Britain%20absorbs%20and%20adapts%20external%20influences.%20Chicken%20%3Cem%3Etikka%20%3C%2Fem%3Eis%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F60553%2Fhistory-biryani-india%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ean%20Indian%20dish%3C%2Fa%3E.%20The%20%3Cem%3Emasala%20%3C%2Fem%3Esauce%20was%20added%20to%20satisfy%20the%20desire%20of%20British%20people%20to%20have%20their%20meat%20served%20in%20gravy.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20was%20followed%20by%20another%20attempt%20in%202009%20to%20pin%20the%20dish%E2%80%99s%20origin%20to%20Europe%20when%20Mohammad%20Sarwar%2C%20then%20Labour%20MP%20for%20Glasgow%20Central%2C%20campaigned%20for%20the%20dish%20to%20be%20given%20EU%20Protected%20Designation%20of%20Origin%20status.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20the%20motion%20was%20tabled%20by%20the%20House%20of%20Commons.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ciframe%20referrerpolicy%3D%5C%22strict-origin-when-cross-origin%5C%22%20allowfullscreen%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fembed%2FTzYACT9nT7A%3Fsi%3Dl7zeE0Cp3SioKMoC%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22560%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22YouTube%20video%20player%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22315%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fiframe%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIf%20you%20were%20starting%20to%20think%20that%20the%20war%20of%20chicken%20%3Cem%3Etikka%20masala%3C%2Fem%3E%E2%80%99s%20origins%20were%20just%20between%20the%20two%20subcontinents%20(India%20and%20Europe)%2C%20you%20are%20wrong.%20Even%20within%20India%2C%20the%20origin%20stands%20to%20be%20debated%20%E2%80%94%20is%20it%20Mogul%20or%20%3Cem%3EPunjabi%3C%2Fem%3E%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EZaeemuddin%20Ahmad%20of%20the%20iconic%20Karim%E2%80%99s%20restaurant%20in%20Delhi%2C%20is%20of%20the%20first%20opinion%2C%20saying%20the%20recipe%20was%20passed%20down%20through%20the%20generations%20in%20his%20family.%20As%20he%20relayed%20to%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Daily%20Telegraph%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20%E2%80%9CChicken%20%3Cem%3Etikka%20masala%3C%2Fem%3E%20is%20an%20authentic%20Mughlai%20recipe%20prepared%20by%20our%20forefathers%20who%20were%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F157345%2Fmughal-emperor-mughlai-food-history-india-news%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eroyal%20chefs%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20the%20Mughal%20period.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMeanwhile%2C%20food%20critic%20Rahul%20Verma%20claims%20to%20have%20first%20tasted%20chicken%20%3Cem%3Etikka%20masala%3C%2Fem%3E%20in%201971%20and%20insists%20it%20is%20a%20%3Cem%3EPunjabi%20%3C%2Fem%3Edish.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20belief%20is%20shared%20by%20many%20who%20see%20the%20chicken%20%3Cem%3Etikka%20masala%20%3C%2Fem%3Eas%20a%20mutation%20of%20the%20butter%20chicken%2C%20which%20is%20(and%20this%20is%20set%20in%20stone)%20the%20creation%20of%20Kundan%20Lal%20Gujral%2C%20the%20man%20behind%20Moti%20Mahal%20restaurant%20in%20Delhi.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThough%20look-alikes%2C%20the%20butter%20chicken%20and%20chicken%20%3Cem%3Etikka%20masala%3C%2Fem%3E%20differ%20in%20their%20taste%20palate%20and%20the%20hero%20ingredient%20(aside%20from%20chicken)%20that%20they%20feature%3B%20the%20former%20has%20copious%20amounts%20of%20butter%2C%20and%20a%20sweeter%20taste%2C%20while%20the%20latter%20is%20on%20the%20spicier%20side.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENaved%20Nasir%2C%20executive%20chef%20of%20the%20UK%E2%80%99s%20popular%20Dishoom%20does%20not%20favour%20this%20opinion%20of%20the%20%3Cem%3Etikka%20%3C%2Fem%3Ebeing%20a%20consequence%20of%20the%20butter%20chicken.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20526px)%20100vw%2C%20526px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2F227376692_2808545786