%20thought%20be%20if%20you%20saw%20a%20pretty%20t-shirt%20priced%20at%20Rs%20200%20and%20on%20sale%3F%20%E2%80%9CHow%20cheap!%20Let%20me%20buy%20it.%E2%80%9D%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMadhu%20would%20react%20the%20same%20way%20when%20she%20saw%20such%20offers%20on%20her%20shopping%20expeditions%2C%20not%20just%20in%20India%20but%20also%20in%20Bangladesh%20and%20Pakistan%2C%20where%20she%20was%20working%20with%20NGOs%20championing%20change%20at%20grassroot%20levels%20in%20underserved%20communities.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHer%20experiences%20gave%20her%20an%20insight%20into%20supply%20chains%20and%20the%20workings%20of%20economies.%20%E2%80%9CMy%20research%20made%20me%20realise%20that%20what%20we%20call%20%E2%80%98cheap%E2%80%99%20is%20actually%20very%20expensive%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20notes.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EExplaining%20this%20critique%2C%20she%20says%2C%20%E2%80%9CWhile%20a%20product%20may%20seem%20economical%20from%20a%20monetary%20standpoint%2C%20there%20is%20so%20much%20exploitation%20that%20goes%20into%20producing%20certain%20items%2C%20like%20clothes%20for%20example.%20This%20includes%20labour%2C%20the%20many%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F303606%2Fdelhi-boy-nirvaan-somany-turns-old-denim-into-sleeping-bag-for-homeless-during-winter%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Elitres%20of%20water%20wasted%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20and%20the%20unfair%20wages%20paid%20to%20those%20involved.%20If%20you%20look%20at%20it%20from%20this%20perspective%2C%20you%E2%80%99ll%20agree%20that%20nothing%20is%20%E2%80%98cheap%E2%80%99%20even%20when%20it%20appears%20to%20be.%E2%80%9D%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHer%20two-decade-long%20experience%20in%20the%20development%20sector%2C%20during%20which%20she%20was%20associated%20with%20UNICEF%20and%20other%20affluent%20names%2C%20shaped%20her%20way%20of%20thinking%20and%20living.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20size